=head2 Metadata => Str

The JSON metadata elements that you want to use in your identity
provider configuration. Required elements are listed based on the
launch specification of the SMART application. For more information on
all possible elements, see Metadata
(https://build.fhir.org/ig/HL7/smart-app-launch/conformance.html#metadata)
