C<authorization_endpoint>: The URL to the OAuth2 authorization
endpoint.

C<grant_types_supported>: An array of grant types that are supported at
the token endpoint. You must provide at least one grant type option.
Valid options are C<authorization_code> and C<client_credentials>.

C<token_endpoint>: The URL to the OAuth2 token endpoint.

C<capabilities>: An array of strings of the SMART capabilities that the
authorization server supports.

C<code_challenge_methods_supported>: An array of strings of supported
PKCE code challenge methods. You must include the C<S256> method in the
